#META# contentSummary: Panegyric poem addressed to Siman-tov b. Naṣr b. Dāniyāl. The poem is copied across multiple diffent sheets in the following order: Ms.Heb.8333.7, Ms.Heb.8333.10, Ms.Heb.8333.9, Ms.Heb.8333.14. Ms.Heb.8333.7r and 14v were reused with Judeo-Persian notes and quatrains.  
